                >
                  FullStack</b
                > Developer
              </h1>
              <h2 class="text-white pt-18 text-2xl">
                <b>9+</b> years Graphic Designing.<br /><b>2+</b> years Web Developing.
              </h2>
              <p class="text-white text-base py-10">
                Building my version of the web.
                <br />Improving my skills through continuous learning.
              </p>
